name: Quad Ski Hydro Thunder - Free JetSki Racing Game
name_original: Quad Ski Hydro Thunder - Free JetSki Racing Game
description:
Gear up your supercharged jet ski for a wild ride through twisting canals and rivers.
Skill, stunts, and speed is all what you will need there to kick out death-defying tricks, and boost your jet ski to victory.
Ride your jet ski in exotic world locations with amazing details. Start earning cash by collecting the coins all your way and spend them on better Quad Ski Hydro Thunder .

This game truly put your Quad Ski Hydro Thunder skills to the ultimate test.

If you like Quad Ski Hydro Thunder and Hydro Thunder Hurricane you will like this.
